STEP 2 — Create hrms_tools.py with 8 tool functions
==============================================================================
Create file: app/agents/hrms_tools.py  (or app/workflows/hrms_workflow/tools.py if the workflows refactor structure is now in place — check which pattern is used and follow it)

For each tool function:
  - Opens its own SessionLocal at start, closes in `finally`
  - Checks user_context.persona — raises PermissionError if wrong persona
  - Returns a formatted human-readable string (the LLM summarizes it)

CREATOR persona tools:

  tool_create_leave_type(name: str, max_days: int, user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "creator". Calls hrms_store.create_leave_type.

  tool_create_payslip(resource_id: int, pay_month: str, basic: float, allowances: float, deductions: float, user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "creator". Calls hrms_store.create_payslip.
    pay_month format: "YYYY-MM"

FILLER persona tools:

  tool_list_my_leave_balance(user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "reviewer". Uses user_context.user_id as resource_id.
    Calls compute_leave_balance. Returns formatted table.

  tool_request_leave(leave_type_id: int, from_date: str, to_date: str, reason: str, user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "reviewer". Uses user_context.user_id as resource_id.
    Validates: from_date <= to_date.
    Calls create_leave_request.

  tool_my_payslip(pay_month: str, user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "reviewer". Uses user_context.user_id as resource_id.
    Calls list_payslips. If no result, returns "No payslip found for that month".

  tool_list_my_leave_requests(user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "reviewer". Uses user_context.user_id as resource_id.
    Calls list_leave_requests. Returns all requests for this user (any status).

APPROVER persona tools:

  tool_list_pending_leaves(user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "approver".
    Calls list_leave_requests with is_approved="PENDING". Returns formatted table.

  tool_decide_leave(request_id: int, decision: str, remarks: str, user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "approver".
    decision: "APPROVED" or "REJECTED".
    Calls approve_leave_request with approver_id from user_context.user_id.

  tool_view_any_payslip(resource_id: int, pay_month: str, user_context: dict) -> str
    Requires persona == "approver".
    Calls list_payslips. Used when approver wants to see a team member's payslip.

